Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在圣所的录音\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is the recording from Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－这是什么    －一段祷文\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What is it? - A prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住   钴队到底在哪里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Stand down! - Where is COBALT Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给予你们祝福 致远星的人们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}"I bring you blessings, people of Reach."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰 117已被解除外勤资格\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John-117 is relieved from active duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他通过精神评估之前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and will be confined to barracks till such time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得离开军营\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}as he clears a psychiatric evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们给改了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They changed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我来时无有慈悲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}"Know that I have come without mercy."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心约翰的精神健康状况吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you have concerns about John's mental state?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管采取什么行动 我所有的模拟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}All of my simulations return the same result,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都反馈回了相同的结果\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}regardless of any action taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么能做的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So there's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无有怜悯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}"Without pity."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟有人几天前袭击了钻队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant element hit COBALT Team days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以假设星盟舰队就在不远处\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We can assume the Covenant Fleet isn't far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们现在不能和他们交于－我们只能反击\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- We're not gonna fight. - We're going to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们赢不了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're just not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我们说话这会儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Essential assets are being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要资产正被运出这颗星球\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}transported off the planet as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能指望你吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是灭亡你们的工具\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}"Know that I am the instrument of your extinction."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找佩雷斯下士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to speak with Corporal Perez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将此星球\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}"I bring this planet forth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献为燔祭\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}as a burnt offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于这祭坛上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Upon this altar,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放上恶魔的头颅\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I place the head of the Demon."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过还有别的生活方式\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You said there were other ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝圣我的人民伟大的旅程\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}"And consecrate the Great Journey of my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是瓦尔加塔奈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am Var 'Gatanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是 死神\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来点夜宵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Got a little late-night supper here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 本尼  詹妮\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hello, Benny. Uh, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 莱尼\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hello, Lenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基斯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Keith.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 你们有什么毛病吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Whoa, whoa, whoa. Settle down. What's up with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够你们所有鸟吃的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去 快进去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go inside! Go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－这边走     －我要回家\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- This way. - I need to get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩雷斯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Perez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去看看我的家人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to see my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我得去找我的家人    －嘿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I need to get to my family! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下士 他们走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Corporal! They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 我得去找我的家人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let me go! I need to see my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点 这边 快点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on! Come on! This way! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我说你刚刚没感觉到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't try to tell me you didn't feel that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面出事了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Something's going on out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们在打仗吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're aware there's a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是遥远的殖民地在打\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In the outer colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战争\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, that's the thing about war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它永远不会停留在战争开始的地方\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It never stays where you put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你 索伦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It is good to see you, Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也很高兴知道你还活着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To know you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我不知道该说什么！－这倒是新鲜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I don't know what to say. - Well, that's unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很了解我吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在脑了里想了上干遍了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I've played this over in my head a thousand times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该说些什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能再和你共外一室我会怎么做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What I would do if I were ever in the same room with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的个头比我记忆中的要小\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're smaller than I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是有好处的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's your upside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,场区外围可能还带电\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The field perimeter may still be charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足以置你于死地 索伦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's more than enough to kill you, Soren!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头见\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人怎么办\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What about these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们得告诉他们 －没时间了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- We have to tell them. - No time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专注执行任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Focus on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持警惕 做好你的工作\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stay alert. Do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是陆战队员 好吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Those weren't Marines, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的家 他们是我的朋友\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This was my family! My friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,训练里可没有这一项\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's no training for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得回舰队司令部\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to get back to FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿我的装备\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Find my gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和防御部队联系\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Link up with the defensive force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是非得来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You don't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们得离开这里 －什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- We need to get out of here. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了 你们得赶紧离开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're coming. You need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们得赶紧离开 这里不安全\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You need to get out of here! It's not safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们得赶紧走 快点 你们得赶紧离开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You gotta leave, come on! You need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你们得赶紧离开 －佩雷斯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You need to get out of here. - Perez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队司令部 快点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}FLEETCOM. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－他们需要知道 他们需要－不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- They need to know. They need-- - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边 快来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This way! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想出去 就走这条路\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you want to get out, it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对这里了如指学 相信我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know this place. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们跟过来了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are they coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放松\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看着你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I watch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么多等离子弹到处乱飞\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}All that plasma flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡就在你身边\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Death all around you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你却\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you never...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这么个女人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}there was this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她抛硬币\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She flipped a coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她问我敢不敢猜 我猜了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She dared me to call it, and I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连续十一次都对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Eleven times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－真幸运－也许吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Lucky. - Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是猜的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But I wasn't guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直如此\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次我上战场 我都知道我可能会失去一些人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Every time I go into battle, I know I can lose somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不会是我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know it's not gonna be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉一定很不错吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并没有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 请小心点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh. Please be careful with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把斧头已经有600多年的历史了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That axe is over 600 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球上曾有人用它砍过树\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Someone on Earth cut trees with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好用市头来做燃料\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Used the wood for fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 大块头\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You. Big man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台打字机\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That typewriter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它对我来说太重了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's too heavy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 这座城市正在遭到袭击\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ma'am, the city's under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就干点事儿 打字机 放上去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, be useful. The typewriter, up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得赶紧离开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的工作室\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这一个地方待了 40年左右\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Same place for 40 years, give or take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 放最上面的架子 麻烦了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look, top shelf, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下士说得对 女士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The corporal's right, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不安全\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This location is not secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在去舰队司令部的路上 我们可以带你一起去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're on our way to FLEETCOM. We can take you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那谁来照看我的东西呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And who'll look after all my stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 这些都不重要\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ma'am, all of this doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个安德伍德便携机械打字机\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's an Underwood standard portable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十世纪的东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Twentieth century.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自康涅狄格州哈特福德\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hartford, Connecticut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在地球上 亲爱的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's Earth, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它经历了六次战争\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's seen six wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见识过共产主义 法西斯主义\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}还有所有介于这两者之间的主义\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Fought communism, fascism, all the isms in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且幸存了下来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And it survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 如果这都不重要的话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now, if that doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟马上就到了 女士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant is on the way, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在人们说话的样子就好像什么都不重要\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}People nowadays talk like nothing matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们是谁呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果什么都不重要 那我们也不重要\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If nothing matters, then we don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士 他们要把这颗星球玻璃化\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ma'am, they're gonna glass the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都将不复存在 你无法幸存\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Nothing will survive. You will not survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－女士 你明白吗－她明白的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Ma'am, do you understand? - She understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 你的秘密地牢吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is this? Your secret dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,监禁是次要目的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Incarceration is a secondary purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这主要是一个实验\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's principally an experimentation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及审讯场所\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and interrogation site.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅限海军情报局访问\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}ONI access only.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是地牢呗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So, like a dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们越来越近了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 给我讲讲凯斯勒吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me, what's Kessler like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他多大了 他大概9岁或者10岁了吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How old is he? He must be 9 or 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我打赌他崇拜你 －别说了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I bet he worships you. - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你那么大的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When you were that age,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是想要溜走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you were always trying to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爬墙钻洞\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Climbing, tunneling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和你谈我儿子的事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't want to talk to you about my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父母就是会谈论自己的孩了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, that's what parents talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少别人是这么告诉我的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}or so I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有个孩子\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You had a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 很自然地 我很想知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So, naturally, I'm curious to know how much of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对他的影响有多大\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}has found its way into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感兴趣纯粹是科学方面的原因\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}My interest is purely scientific.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扯蛋\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们这是要去哪吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you even know where we're headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我当然知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当时是最积极的那个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you were the most driven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人是被招募进来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The others had to be recruited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你是说绑架来的吧 －但你是自愿的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Kidnapped. - But you wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我第一次见到你开始\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Right from the very first time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就想当斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You wanted to be a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我当时 6岁 -没错 你当时才6岁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I was 6. - Yes, you were 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你已经知道了自己的目标\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And you already knew your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个天生的战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You were a born warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－即便在你出了事故之后 你 －我的什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Even after your accident, you-- - My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手臂\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放你离开真的很不容易\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It was very difficult to let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放我离开吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我逃离了你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I escaped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我从你手里幸存了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I survived you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有了生活\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I made a life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便还有阴魂不散的你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}in spite of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看这是一个很好的故事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I suppose that's as good a story as any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是等离子伤\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Plasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等离了伤\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Plasma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－他们来了－拿着这个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- They're here. - Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好别在背后向我开枪\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And try not to shoot me in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我没法保证\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放低身体\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stay low!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤  撤  撤\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－快走 快走 －走 走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Go! Go! - Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在从舰队司令部撤退\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're evacuating people from FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不安全\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're no good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Go, go, go, go! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你别介意 我们没等你就开始了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I hope you don't mind, we got started without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我需要武器 －自己拿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I need a weapon! - Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你还好吗 －现在好得不行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You good? - I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们尝试攻下舰队司令部\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Trying to get to FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但撞见了大约20个精英战士 他们一直在猛攻\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ran into about 20 Elites. They just keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和其他小队有联系吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Any contact with the other units?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 他们抢先破坏了通讯系统\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, they took out the comms first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持续火力输出 我保护你的后方\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Keep making that noise. I'll find your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We gotta move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有办法绕过星盟的阵地吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Any idea how we're gonna get around this Covenant position?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不绕过去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're not going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 给我五个陆战队员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}All right. Give me five Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们开始向桥头堡旁的掩蔽处移动\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The rest of you are gonna lay down cover fire
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人准备提供掩护火力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}while we traverse to the defilade by the bridgehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一进去 其他人立刻撤退\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Once we get inside, everybody else fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退到哪里 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To where, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里需要去哪里 别在这里就行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Wherever you're needed. Just not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你知道你在干什么吗 －我和你一起去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What do you think you're doing? - I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不行 路易 你不许去－我不需要你批准\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- No, Louis, you're not. - I don't need your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去 我可以救助伤员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm coming too. I can help with the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我们走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 准备好了吗     跟着你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Hey, you ready? - On your go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火力掩护   准备好了吗   走吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cover fire! Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 还有你跟着我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You and you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们打中他了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 继续前进\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on! Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三点方向\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放低身体 快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stay low! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑 快 快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Move! Go! Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快走吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Moving! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背后接敌\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Contact rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在掩护    补位\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Reloading! - Covering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心手雷\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Frag out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}On me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 快走 快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了 快点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We gotta move. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没事了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达尼洛在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's Danilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达尼洛在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's Danilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹 达尼洛在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz! Where's Danilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他阵亡了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亡魂\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Wraith! - Wraith!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火力掩护\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get some cover fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点   路易\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Come on! - Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝这个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Gotta move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我该待的地方\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm right where I need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子就在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你个大礼包\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I got something for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 路易\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No! Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么鬼地方\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What the hell is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有别的囚犯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're not the only prisoners here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说自己知道出去的路吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought you said you knew a way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科塔娜吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cortana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔西医生     对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Dr. Halsey. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退回来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹 穿上战甲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz, get suited up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 等等\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么去打仗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you just gonna go off to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一句话都不留下吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}without saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 谢谢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay, well... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看运气如何\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}For luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉毁了你的休息日 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry to ruin your day off, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, I'm happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在清理下层\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I've been clearing out the lower levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在防御工事建起来之前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Few of those cloaked Elites snuck in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有几个隐形精英偷偷溜进来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}before the barricades went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀外星人我都快杀吐了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm almost sick of killing aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还能坚持\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－里兹 你还好吗－凯在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Hey, Riz, you all right? - Where's Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想问你呢 她肯定还在外面\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was gonna ask the same thing. She must still be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我对凯的了解 她去猎杀星盟了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, if I know Kai, she went hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也应该这样做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We should do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要去穿战甲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're just going to get suited up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战甲没了 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The armor's gone, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的装备 战甲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Our suits. The armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不在那里    狗娘养的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's not there. - Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克森在哪儿     我不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Where's Ackerson? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥部撤退了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Command bugged out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高级人员也跟着走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They took high-ranking personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贵的资产   他们拿走了我们的装备\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Valuable assets. - They took our suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长 这到底是怎么回事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief, what the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在指挥\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who's in command?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－再给我们找点装备 －收到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Get us more kit. - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,降低齐射率 为我们多争取一点时间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Reduce rate of the salvos, buy us a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到  长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Copy that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你爆破之间 我希望舰桥上的这群混蛋\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I want as many of those bastards on the bridge as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越多越好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}before you blow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在上面   长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm on it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们拿走了我们的战甲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They took our suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我内心里还小小地希望你已经死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know, part of me was hoping that you were dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就不用听你说 我早告诉过你了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}so I wouldn't have to listen to this "I told you so."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕你没那么走运 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No such luck, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队在维舍格勒殉职了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cobalt was KIA at Visegrad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼看到了尸体\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw the bodies myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至不知道是什么攻击了自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They never knew what hit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的两把武器都是满匣满弹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Two of their weapons had full mags.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未发一弹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Didn't get a shot off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维舍格勒沦陷时 还留下了一个盲区\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When Visegrad went down, it left a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法知道有多少星盟部队登陆了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's no way of knowing how many Covenant landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经演变成陆战了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's a ground game for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在袭击发电站\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're hitting the power stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.06,0:24:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在全力保护剩下电站 如果没有它们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're defending the ones that we can, but without them--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－磁力加速炮就哑火了－没错\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- MAC-array goes down. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轨道防御灰飞烟灭\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No more orbital defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟舰队可以长驱直入\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant fleet can move into range.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－然后玻璃化－差不多就是这个结果\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Then the glassing begins. - That's about the size of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提利尔 天蝎号在东边机库\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tyrell, Scorpion in the east hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－把 它开到舰桥上吧 －是 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Let's get it on the bridge. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.43,0:24:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们的舰队呢 他们在哪里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What about our fleet? Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.39,0:24:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得上级的决策是要保存\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I believe the determination was made to preserve
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.56,0:24:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们最重要的军事资产\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}our most essential military assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.17,0:24:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.17,0:24:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让致远星沦陷吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just let Reach fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.65,0:24:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道会发生这样的事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They knew this was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.22,0:24:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们早就预见到这种结果 于是做了权衡\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They saw it coming, they did the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.88,0:24:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.31,0:24:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 当权者\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know. The powers that be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军部 情报部 随你挑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Admiralty. The ONI. Take your pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.97,0:24:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－是艾克森吗 －沒错\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Ackerson? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.93,0:24:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也改变不了这里的情况\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Doesn't change the situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.89,0:24:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我说清楚 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let me be clear John.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不在乎他们的算盘\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't give a shit about their calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要星盟为这个星球的每一寸土地付出代价\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm gonna make the Covenant pay for every inch of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.50,0:25:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在的任务是疏散尽可能多的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Our mission now is to evacuate as many people as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.59,0:25:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where do you want me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.77,0:25:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在策划一个阻击点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're creating a choke point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.39,0:25:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然寡不敌众 但如果我们能集中兵力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're outnumbered, but if we can concentrate our forces--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.91,0:25:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I get it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.43,0:25:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像在塞莫皮莱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thermopylae.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.92,0:25:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的耳朵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}My ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.09,0:25:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被手榴弹波及就这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Grenades will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.71,0:25:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你放手好吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can I have my hand back?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.76,0:25:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的放我离开 是什么意思\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What do you mean, you let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.63,0:25:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道刚才里面发生了什么吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you have any idea what just happened in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.07,0:25:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人拿走了科塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Our enemy is in possession of Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才什么意思\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.55,0:25:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了你的潜力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw your potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.16,0:25:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量 你的专注\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your strength, your focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.82,0:25:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都指望着你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They all looked to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.43,0:25:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰指望着你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John looked to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.87,0:26:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的强化手术失败后 我需要他靠自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}After your augmentation failed, I needed him to look to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.87,0:26:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这样的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, that's not what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.79,0:26:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然为什么你逃跑那天夜里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why do you think there was no one guarding the ships
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.83,0:26:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人看守船只\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}the night you ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.27,0:26:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得赶紧上去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We need to get up there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.34,0:26:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我一下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Help me with that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.35,0:26:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.96,0:26:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得把这些人运走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We've got to get these people out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.05,0:26:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运输飞船从上层机库起飞\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Transports are leaving from the upper hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.44,0:26:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.61,0:26:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.27,0:26:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.10,0:26:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠着我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.53,0:26:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开 让一让 让一让\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Clear the way! Coming through! Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Clear the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.63,0:27:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.24,0:27:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么指示 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are your orders, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.77,0:27:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着我的帽子\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hold my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.95,0:27:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冈尼\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Gunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.21,0:27:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲板上全体注意\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Attention all on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.04,0:27:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它带进来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.69,0:27:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面中间 跑步走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Front and center! Double time!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.40,0:27:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道我看到了什么吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know what I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.14,0:27:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的是一群不好惹的陆战队员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I see some hard-ass Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.97,0:27:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有看到疑虑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What I do not see is doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.36,0:27:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这间屋子里没有看到失败\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I do not see defeat in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.32,0:27:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有看到投降\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I do not see surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.85,0:27:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.55,0:27:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着你们的脸\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When I look at your faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.38,0:27:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了我们种族最好的一面\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I see the very best of who we are as a people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.34,0:28:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用勇气战斗  用心战斗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You fought with courage. You fought with heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.38,0:28:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用爱战斗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You fought with love
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.82,0:28:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了并肩作战的兄弟姐妹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}for your brothers and sisters in arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.56,0:28:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们每一个人都不再需要证明任何事情\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's nothing left for any one of you to prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.52,0:28:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我见过的最优秀的陆战队员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're the finest Marines I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.96,0:28:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们值得知道真相\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And you deserve the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.58,0:28:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军就在门口了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The enemy is at our gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.23,0:28:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数量碾压我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Their numbers are overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抵挡得了一时 抵挡不了一世\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We will not be able to hold them back forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.07,0:28:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们站在一起的陆战队员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Any Marine who makes this stand with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.85,0:28:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都难逃一死\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}will not survive the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.25,0:28:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们不是一个人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But you will not make that stand alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.13,0:28:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.43,0:28:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.31,0:29:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸地为大家介绍约翰 -117\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It is my honor to introduce to you John-117.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.49,0:29:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know him as Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天 他不需要盔甲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Today, he needs no armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.50,0:29:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天 他只需要内心的战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Today, all he needs is the warrior inside of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.63,0:29:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们每一个人心中都有同样的战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And it's the same warrior that's in each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.81,0:29:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个愿意为家园牺牲生命的战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The one that is willing to lay down your life for your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.38,0:29:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多拖住敌人一刻\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}For every moment that we hold the enemy at bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.64,0:29:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能有更多的无辜平民登上运输飞船逃离\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}more innocent people can escape on the transports.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.60,0:29:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们安全离开后 会向外讲述\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And when they do, they will go forth
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.61,0:29:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们今天谱写的故事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and tell the story that you write today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.70,0:29:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们将会被铭记 你们是勇敢的女性和男性\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You will be remembered as the brave women and men
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.70,0:29:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲自己的生命 让我们的孩了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}who laid down their lives so that one day our children
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.79,0:29:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无需生活在战争怪物的阴影下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}may live without fear of this monster we call war.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.67,0:29:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 就让这些铁甲混账看看\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now, show those scaly bastards
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.76,0:30:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们惹错星球了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}they fucked with the wrong planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.77,0:30:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解散\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Fall out!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.21,0:30:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Take your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.55,0:30:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解散 列队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Fall out! Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远忠诚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Semper fi!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.78,0:30:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I am glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.18,0:30:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 长官    不 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Yes, sir. - No, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.05,0:30:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很重要\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.01,0:30:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的通讯器 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your comms, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.97,0:30:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通讯器 上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Comms, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.19,0:30:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.62,0:30:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看我在干什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What does it look like I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.23,0:30:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候 职级啥也不是了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stripes don't mean shit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.15,0:30:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－把我枪拿来  －不 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Get me my gun. - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.80,0:30:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能失去你 这还不是结束\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We can't afford to lose you. This won't be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.98,0:30:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天过后 还有许多仗要打\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's more fight to come after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.85,0:30:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要像你这样的好人来领导我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're gonna need good people like you to lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.77,0:30:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰 我在这里也会给你们下达指令的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John, I'm still giving the orders here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.99,0:30:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你能一直掌握指挥权\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And we need you to keep giving the orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.03,0:30:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就给了艾克森那样的人可乘之机了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}or else it's gonna be people like Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.99,0:30:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在拜托 把平民转移出去吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now please, get those civilians out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.26,0:31:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.43,0:31:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在我该在的地方\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm where I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.14,0:31:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好把握\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Make it count.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.93,0:31:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You bet your ass, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.63,0:31:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把弹药均匀分布\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get this ammo evenly distributed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.07,0:31:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－就这里 各位 －好的 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Right here, guys. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.29,0:31:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锁定装弹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Lock and load!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.86,0:31:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特雷尔\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tyrell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.69,0:31:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让火力小组准备好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Got your fire team set?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.91,0:31:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Roger that, Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.74,0:31:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－火力小组 －好了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Fire team! - All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.43,0:31:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持各区域火力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Maintain your sectional fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.53,0:32:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪炮准备好了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Guns are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.37,0:32:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁能让我看看桥塔的情况\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Somebody get me vis on that bridgehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.46,0:32:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.51,0:32:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 雅各布\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hello, Jacob.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.21,0:32:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.83,0:32:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想多嘴\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I hate to interrupt whatever the hell this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.79,0:32:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们谁能给我指一条\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but could either of you point me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.01,0:32:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开这鬼地方的最快的路\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}in the quickest way off this hellhole?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.05,0:32:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上层机库有平民运输飞船准备起飞\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's a civilian transport leaving from the upper hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.75,0:32:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是平民\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.93,0:32:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是海盗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.59,0:32:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小企业主\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Small business owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.21,0:33:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在哪呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where the hell are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.65,0:33:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天蝎 3X 我是银队1号\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Scorpion-Three X-Ray, this is Silver-One.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.09,0:33:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请讲 银队 完毕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go ahead, Silver. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.91,0:33:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给桥头打一炮白磷 完毕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Give me one round of white phos on that bridgehead, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.26,0:33:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上打 完毕 威利·皮特\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Copy. One round, Willy Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.92,0:33:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射 完毕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sending it. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.88,0:33:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还叫不醒他们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That'll wake 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.75,0:33:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我草 开火\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, shit. Light 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达在这里吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is Miranda here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.37,0:33:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在 谢天谢地\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No. Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.99,0:33:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.64,0:33:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不能说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry, I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.56,0:33:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开间房吧你俩\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.21,0:33:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和这人在一起\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What exactly are you doing with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.56,0:33:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}person?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.91,0:34:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三分钟 前我还是个海盗呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Three minutes ago, I was a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.79,0:34:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有进步\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm making progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.70,0:34:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把科塔娜拿走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They have Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.88,0:34:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－星盟 －我亲眼看着他们拿走了她\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- The Covenant? - I saw them take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.32,0:34:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个向斐力和马吉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A Sangheili and Makee.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.63,0:34:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马吉死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Makee's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.11,0:34:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显然没有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.55,0:34:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下士 把这些人带上船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Corporal, get these people on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.12,0:34:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在带了 长官 快快快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Trying, sir. Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.99,0:34:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点    一秒也不能浪费\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on! Every second counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.55,0:34:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快快快 快一点 快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on, come on. Faster! Come on, come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.17,0:34:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快快快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.25,0:34:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一班了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is this the last shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.13,0:34:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.47,0:34:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听见什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.05,0:34:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.92,0:34:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.37,0:35:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.29,0:35:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.18,0:35:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是凯斯上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is Admiral Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.05,0:35:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上层机库受到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Upper hangar is under attack
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.36,0:35:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多支星盟队伍袭击 完毕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}from multiple Covenant units, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.23,0:35:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运输飞船载满了平民\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That transport's full of civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.33,0:35:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们帮你们争取点时间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We'll buy you some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.63,0:35:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,途中掩护\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cover on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.11,0:35:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.20,0:35:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快   快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Move it! - Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.81,0:35:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火力小队来中间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Fire team in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.47,0:36:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 海军陆战队   你明白了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on, Marines! You got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.26,0:36:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.79,0:36:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平民都上船了 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Civilians are all on board, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.36,0:36:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.89,0:36:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.68,0:36:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上回来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.03,0:36:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能飞吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can you fly this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.38,0:36:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得在啊 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not without you on it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.42,0:36:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会回来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.90,0:37:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去帮他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We have to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.12,0:37:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 帮不了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No. We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.17,0:37:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.65,0:37:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩雷斯下士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Corporal Perez?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.87,0:37:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.74,0:37:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Punch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.96,0:37:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't do that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.44,0:37:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.88,0:37:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 放开我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.19,0:37:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅各布\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Jacob!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.19,0:37:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.98,0:38:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有火吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Got a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.60,0:38:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.86,0:39:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我起来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.00,0:39:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方突破防线\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Form up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.21,0:39:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.87,0:39:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突破\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Breach!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.14,0:40:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.91,0:41:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.23,0:41:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.76,0:41:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.98,0:41:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时候未到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.88,0:42:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No!


